Designed for large organisations with complex operations
Covers logistics, sustainability, and data-heavy processes

**Features
Full waste lifecycle management
Route optimisation and fleet tracking
Advanced reporting and analytics
Integration with business systems (ERP)
Sustainability and carbon tracking

**Website / UX
Structured layout (not long scrolling)
Clear top navigation with dropdown menus
Content split across multiple pages
Strong use of dashboards and data visuals
Call-to-action buttons placed early (e.g. “Book a demo”)
Overall feel: corporate, structured, data-focused

**Strengths
Highly scalable
Strong analytics capabilities
Trusted by large organisations

**Weaknesses
